  28 Sep 2011; Arun Raghavan <ford_prefect@gentoo.org>
  padevchooser-0.9.3-r1.ebuild:
  Block being built against >=media-sound/pulseaudio-1.0. padevchooser is
  considered deprecated by upstreamd and will eventually be removed.

  30 Jan 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  padevchooser-0.9.3-r1.ebuild, +files/padevchooser-0.9.3-libnotify-0.7.patch:
  Fix building with x11-libs/libnotify >= 0.7.

  08 Mar 2010; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org>
  padevchooser-0.9.3-r1.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug #305923

  08 Mar 2010; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org>
  padevchooser-0.9.3-r1.ebuild:
  remove inexistant file from dodoc call

  08 Mar 2010; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org>
  padevchooser-0.9.3-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #305923

